name: KEM Open Source
body:
### Welcome to KEM Open Source
KEM release open source code to help you take full advantage of our fulfilment services.

## Repos
# Doku

Doku, Swahili for *shop*, is a fully functional eCommerce website fully using the KEM Api. Hosted on bitbucket to allow free, private forks, it is released under the MIT license.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
